  <description><![CDATA[<h2><span data-contrast="auto"><span class="TextRun SCXW105249196 BCX8" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW105249196 BCX8">The city of Bergen is a fantastic starting point for any trip </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW105249196 BCX8">to</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW105249196 BCX8"> Norway,</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW105249196 BCX8"> with plenty of cultural and historical sites to see as well as walking trails. </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW105249196 BCX8">Flam </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW105249196 BCX8">or </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW105249196 BCX8">Aurland sit on the edge of one of the branches of the Sognefjord</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW105249196 BCX8">, although they’re not far apart, they both have something slightly unique to offer, </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW105249196 BCX8">so you can choose which village suits you best.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW105249196 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}"> </span></span></h2>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">This is the perfect multi-centre holiday for those looking to see the sights of <a data-udi="umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5}" title="Bergen" data-anchor="#">Bergen</a> and then head inland to explore the famous fjords of <a data-udi="umb://document/18b94b9d5f4d4510a6c23eecf8a70de1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/18b94b9d5f4d4510a6c23eecf8a70de1}" title="Flam &amp; Aurland" data-anchor="#">Flam or Aurland</a>.  </span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}"> </span></p>
<p><strong>Guide price from: £1,3780pp*</strong></p>
<p><strong>Your multi-centre holiday options:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A choice of durations in your chosen hotels</li>
<li><span data-contrast="auto">Any day arrivals</span></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Your holiday includes:  </strong><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}"> </span></p>
<ul>
<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="2" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;multilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">Return flights from the UK</span></li>
<li>Return airport transfers (direct) to and from your chosen hotels</li>
<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="2" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;multilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">Ferry from Bergen to Flam or Aurland through the Sognefjord</span></li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to Book Your Multi-Centre Holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Simply give us a call to book your multi-centre holiday. Flights, hotel and transport? Consider it done. Dial in and let our experts plan your dream getaway. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
<p><em>*Prices are based on 2 people sharing for 4 nights in a Twin Room at Thon Hotel Brsitol Bergen, Bergen, and 3 nights in a Standard Room at Fretheim Hotel, Flam in a Standard Room with ferry transfers between resorts, departing on the 1st of June 25 from London Gatwick airport. Supplements for alternative flights, flight routes, and room types may apply. Prices are correct at the time of publishing on 21/11/24 but are subject to change based on availability. Please call for the most up-to-date pricing and availability before booking.</em></p>]]></description>
